MSad = function(spec) {
var that = {};
that.getSite = function(){return spec.site};
that.getArea = function(){return spec.area};
that.getDivName = function(){return spec.divName};
that.getRefresh = function(){return spec.refresh};
that.getSize = function(){return spec.size};
that.getTargeting = function(){return spec.targeting};
that.addTargeting = function(target, value){spec.targeting[target] = value};
that.report = function() {
if (typeof(_Anemone) != 'undefined') {
var adReportingParams = { size: that.getSize(), 
action: 'display', 
provider: 'doubleclick', 
campaign: that.getSite() + '/' + that.getArea()
};
if (that.getTargeting().source) {adReportingParams.partner = that.getTargeting().source; }
if (that.getTargeting().uid) {adReportingParams.anxui = that.getTargeting().uid; }
if (that.getTargeting().pos) {adReportingParams.placement = that.getTargeting().pos; }
_Anemone.logEvent('Ad', adReportingParams);
}
};
return that;
};
MSads = { 
ads : [],
gAdsToRefresh : [],
reportRefresh : function() {
for (ad in this.ads) {
if (this.ads.hasOwnProperty(ad)) {
if (this.ads[ad].getRefresh()) {
this.ads[ad].report();
}
}
}
}
};

    <script type="text/javascript">
	$(document).ready(function(){
		$.ajax({
                    url: 'http://common.webfetti.com/country/ip.jsonp',
                    dataType: 'jsonp',
                    success: function(result){
                        $('.signup-form select option[value="'+ result.data.countryCode +'"]').prop('selected',true);
                        GW.facebook.countryCode = result.data.countryCode;
                        if (result.data.countryCode == 'CA') {
                             GW.facebook.isEmailOptInConfirmed = false;
                        	 $('.signup-form input[name="reg-internal"]').prop('checked',false);
                        }
                    }
                });
		$('.signup-button, .signin-button').click(function() {
			var countryParam = location.search.replace("?", "");
	    	if (countryParam.length > 0 && ( countryParam.split("=")[0].indexOf('country') != -1) && countryParam.split("=")[1] === 'CA') {
	    		$('.signup-form select option[value="CA"]').prop('selected',true);
	    		GW.facebook.countryCode = 'CA';
	    		GW.facebook.isEmailOptInConfirmed = false;
	    		$('.signup-form input[name="reg-internal"]').prop('checked',false);
	    	}
		});
	});
    </script>	<form id="login-modal" style="display: none;">

<script type='text/javascript'>
if (!document.querySelector) { 
	(function (d, s) {
		var styleEl = document.createElement('STYLE'); 
		//IE6 fix document.head not available
		var documentHead = document.head || document.getElementsByTagName('head')[0]; 
		documentHead.appendChild(styleEl); 
		d = document, s = styleEl.sheet || styleEl.styleSheet; //IE6 fix styleEl.sheet not available 
		d.querySelectorAll = function (r, c, i, j, a) { 
			a = d.all, c = [], r = r.split(','); 
			for (i = r.length; i--;) { 
				if (s.insertRule) {   //IE6 fix styleEl.sheet css_sheet.insertRule not available
					s.insertRule(r[i] + '{k:v }', 0);
				} else if (s.addRule) { 
					s.addRule(r[i], 'k:v'); 
				} 
				for (j = a.length; j--;) a[j].currentStyle.k && c.push(a[j]); 
					s.removeRule(0); 
			} 
			return c; 
		}; 
	})(); 
}

window.removeHtmlElement = function(el) { 
	el.style.display = 'none';
	el.style.visibility = 'hidden'; 
	el.style.opacity = 0; 
	el.style.background = 'none'; 
	el.setAttribute('width', 0); 
	el.setAttribute('height', 0); 
};
function createStyleSheet() {
	var styleEl = document.createElement('STYLE');
	var documentHead = document.head || document.getElementsByTagName('head')[0];  //IE6 fix document.head not available
	documentHead.appendChild(styleEl);
	return  styleEl.sheet || styleEl.styleSheet;  //IE6 fix styleEl.sheet not available
}
function addCSSRule(sheet, selector, rules, index) {
	if(sheet.insertRule){
		sheet.insertRule(selector + '{' + rules + '}', index);
	}
	else if(sheet.addRule) {
		sheet.addRule(selector, rules, index);
	}
}
function removeStyleSheet(sheet) {
	sheet.parentNode.removeChild(sheet);
}
</script>

	
<script type="text/javascript">
	window.MindsparkShowGames = function() {
		var player = $('#game-area-body');
	    var t = setInterval(function(){
	    	if (player.length) {
	                        try {
	                            !t || clearInterval(t);
	                            $.each(window.gameInitHandle||[], function(k, v){
									try{
										v.call(null);
									}catch(_){}
								});
	                            // Some games need to know to play sound, etc., when the ad is done
	                            if (GW.util.isFunction(window.adIsDone)) {
	                                window.adIsDone();
	                            }
								GW.reporting.HeartBeat.start(window.gameReportingInfo, 'game');//Start the heartbeat
	                            GW.reporting.reportGameEvent(window.gameReportingInfo, "preGameAdDone");
	                        } 
	                        catch (_) {}
	          }
	          player = $('#game-area-body');
        }, 5);
	                
        player.show();
	};
</script>

<script type='text/javascript'>
 (function(gameAreaElement){ 
	'use strict';
      var gameArea = document.querySelector(gameAreaElement),
		pregameAdModal = document.querySelector('#pregame-ad-modal'),
		preGameAd = document.querySelector('.pregame-ad'),
		adHeightOffset = 20,
		params = {
			quality : 'high',
			bgcolor : '#000000',
			align : 'middle',
			allowscriptaccess : 'always',
 			allowfullscreen: 'false'
		},

		attributes = { 
 			id : 'preloader',
			name : 'preloader',
			width: 480,
			height: 400
		},

		flashvars = {
			adTagUrl : encodeURIComponent('http://pubads.g.doubleclick.net/gampad/ads?sz=640x480&iu=/23219321/iac.ms-gmgwdl.us.dw&ciu_szs&impl=s&gdfp_req=1&env=vp&output=xml_vast2&unviewed_position_start=1&url=${referrer_url}&description_url=${description_url}&correlator=${timestamp}')
		}, 
		swfUrl = 'http://ak.imgfarm.com/images/adXPreloader/swf/ima3_preloader_1.5.swf',
		offset = {};
		window.MindsparkAdsPreGameAdFinished = function() {
			if (typeof(MindsparkShowGames) == 'function') { 
				MindsparkShowGames(); 
			}
		};

      if(!pregameAdModal || !gameArea || !preGameAd){ 
			return MindsparkAdsPreGameAdFinished();
			if (pregameAdModal) {
				removeHtmlElement(pregameAdModal);
			}
		}
		offset = {width : attributes.width, top : gameArea.getBoundingClientRect().top, left : gameArea.getBoundingClientRect().left };
		var sheet = createStyleSheet();
		addCSSRule(sheet,  gameAreaElement, 'background: white; height : '+ (attributes.height+adHeightOffset) + 'px; width: 100%;', 0);
		addCSSRule(sheet,  '#pregame-ad-modal', 'position: absolute;  width:' +offset.width + 'px; height:'+ (attributes.height+adHeightOffset)+ 'px; top:' + offset.top + 'px; left: ' +offset.left+ 'px; backgroundColor: #000;', 0);
		addCSSRule(sheet,  '.pregame-ad', 'margin: 0; position : absolute; top :10px; left:' +((offset.width/2)-(attributes.width/2))+'px;', 0);
		if (!swfobject.hasFlashPlayerVersion('10.0.0')) {
			gameArea.appendChild('<p><a href="http://www.adobe.com/go/getflashplayer"><img src="http://www.adobe.com/images/shared/download_buttons/get_flash_player.gif" alt="Get Adobe Flash player" /></a></p>');
		}
		window.cleanup = function(){ 
           MindsparkAdsPreGameAdFinished();
			removeHtmlElement(document.getElementById(attributes.id));
			removeHtmlElement(pregameAdModal);
			removeStyleSheet(sheet);
		};

	window.noAdsReturned = window.removeAdSwf = window.cleanup;

	swfobject.embedSWF(swfUrl, 'videoAd', attributes.width, attributes.height, '10.0.0', false, flashvars, params, attributes);
}('#game-area'));
</script>
